# AI Context Configuration - core/

## Directory Purpose
Core pipeline functionality - state management, orchestration, and planning.

## AI Indexing Priority
PRIORITY: HIGH
This is the heart of the pipeline system and should always be indexed for AI context.

## Scope
ACTIVE_CODE - Production code that is actively maintained and central to the system.

## Key Components
- state/ - Database and CRUD operations
- engine/ - Orchestration and execution logic
- planning/ - Workstream generation and archiving
- openspec_parser.py - OpenSpec integration

## Import Pattern
from core.state.db import init_db
from core.engine.orchestrator import Orchestrator
from core.planning.planner import generate_workstream

## When to Use This Section
- Implementing state management features
- Adding orchestration logic
- Modifying workstream planning
- Database schema changes

## Related Sections
- engine/ - Alternative job-based execution (different from core/engine/)
- error/ - Error detection integration
- specifications/ - Spec management
- tests/pipeline/ - Core tests

## Exclude from Context
- __pycache__/
- *.pyc
- .pytest_cache/
